author: Kevin Rawlinson
description: George Cheese, 18, was locked in cage and had his clothes set on fire by colleagues at company in Reading before his death
title: Audi garage not to blame for bullied mechanic killing himself, coroner rules

author: By Stewart Paterson For Mailonline
description: Audi apprentice George Cheese, 18, of Woodley, Reading, was found hanged by a neighbour after he was subjected to horrific abuse by colleagues at a garage, an inquest heard today.
title: An apprentice was found hanged after colleagues 'locked him in cage'
